snippet.title: Seekers: Enlightenment Ivy Lancaster Gameplay
snippet.description:
Hey guys, here is another video of my progress where you play in the main game mode, Story Mode while playing as the first character Ivy Lancaster!

if you are interested in the game, you can Wishlist it on Steam with this link where it will be released at the end of July!

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2486240/Seekers_Enlightenment/
